<p class="ql-align-center">国庆期间到访即送精美国民伴手礼一份</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让你不虚此行！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200928/e18643d9746f494eafdfe25ce75fc28b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
